Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在遙遠的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,早於眾神降臨下界前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.22,0:00:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,便與人類互相爭戰的邪惡存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:14.92,Background,,0,0,0,,找到了 在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,別讓牠跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,人們永遠不會饒恕牠們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,即便是神明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.96,0:00:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,也無法救贖牠們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,龍女?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(943,970)}Vouivre
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.78,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Vouivre：飛龍（Wyvern）的法文拼音。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,人類和怪物是絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,無法 和睦共處的
